<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This trigger event occurs when the inquirer specifies a request for a listing of patient names. This event differs from event I02 (request/receipts of patient selection display list) in that it returns the patient list in repeating PID segments instead of repeating DSP segments.</p>
</div>
